text: It is my daily place routine because i always drop my toddler there for the childcare center. It has a nice ambience and lots of shops
More like neighbourhood mall. Cold Storage has a good wine selection. A few restaurants and cafes that are okay on ground floor.

Lately the renovations have scale up the place
From the entrance to the top floors

Overall changes and adding more stores

Highly recommended to be visited

This mall is pretty quiet in the day. There are restaurants, a bar and a cafe here for dining. There is also a convenience store, which I guess gets most of its patron from nearby drinking establishments at night or from the nearby offices and condos. There are other beauty facilities like haircut, nails and massage, but they look quiet too. Nothing much to see but a short 3 mins walk from Fort Canning MRT.
